node.text: Found out that the ankle injury I got while filming #RealSnow early this season was a little worse than I hoped. And after ignoring it all season I now have to take some time off for it to heal up properly🤕 So my spring adventures will unfortunatley have less snowboarding this year😔 but hopefully back in full soon🤞🏽
